<html>
<body>
<p>
Your organization has been invited by <%=@invitation.inviter.name%> to participate in a CompSage compensation survey.
Taking a few minutes to respond to this survey will get you the survey report for free.  There is no signup required.
<%=link_to 'Take the survey now', survey_login_path(:key => @invitation.key, :only_path => false, :subdomain => subdomain_for(:email => @invitation.email))%>!
If you would like to verify this request, feel free to email the survey sponsor at
<a href="mailto:<%= @survey.sponsor.email %>"><%= @survey.sponsor.email %></a>.
</p>
<p>
  The details of the survey are as follows:
  <br />
  <b>Job Title: </b><%=@survey.job_title%>
  <br />
  <b>Description: </b><%=@survey.description%>
  <br />
  <b>Sponsor: </b><%=@survey.sponsor.name%>
  <br />
  <b>Response deadline: </b><%=better_time_ago_in_words(@survey.end_date)%>
  </p>
<% unless @survey.custom_invitation_message.blank? %>
  <p><b>Sponsor's Message:</b><br />
  <%= simple_format(@survey.custom_invitation_message) %></p>
<% end %>
<p>
  Thanks,
  <br />
  CompSage.com
</p>
</body>
</html>
